      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">12.500</ph> Scope of subpart.</title>
      <body class="- topic/body ">
         <ol id="d708e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d735e10" class="- topic/p ">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph> As
required by <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S. C. 1906</xref> and <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/browse.xhtml;jsessionid=114A3287C7B3359E597506A31FC855B3"
                        format="html"
                        scope="external"
                        class="- topic/xref ">1907</xref>, this subpart
lists provisions of law that are not applicable to-</p>
               <ol id="d708e29" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d735e22" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph> Contracts
for the acquisition of <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial
products or commercial services;<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.500 by—
a. Removing from paragraphs (a)(1) and (2) the term “commercial items” and adding “commercial products or commercial services” in its place;?></ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d735e31" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph> Subcontracts,
at any tier, for the acquisition of <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial products or
commercial services;<?FM MARKER [Why] Amend section 12.500 by—
a. Removing from paragraphs (a)(1) and (2) the term “commercial items” and adding “commercial products or commercial services” in its place;?></ph> and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p id="d735e41" class="- topic/p ">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph> Contracts
and subcontracts, at any tier, for the acquisition <ph class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>of commercially
available off-the-shelf (COTS) items.<?FM MARKER [Why] b. Removing from paragraph (a)(3) the text “of COTS items” and adding “of commercially available off-the-shelf (COTS) items” in its place; and?></ph>
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p id="d735e50" class="- topic/p ">
