or modify their applicability to either contracts or subcontracts
for the acquisition of <ph rev="FAC 2022-01 December 6, 2021" class="- topic/ph "><?FM MARKER [CaseNumber] FAR Case 2018-018?>commercial
products or commercial services.<?FM MARKER [Why] c. Removing from paragraph (b) the term “commercial items” and adding “commercial products or commercial services” in its place.?></ph>
               </p>
            </li>
